childMarkdownRemark.html:
gatsby-theme-cooper-hewitt

A child theme of gatsby-theme-blog.

Create a site from the starter:

gatsby new new-blog https://github.com/KyleAMathews/gatsby-starter-theme-cooper-hewitt
cd new-blog
gatsby develop
